
Description
-----------

A simple script that grabs a list of active maildirs, then compares that list
to a list of maildirs on the filesystem. Any filesystem maildirs that are not
in the database will be moved to a backup directory.

Usage
-----

Edit the script settings within the script at the top. Then just run it in the
command line or setup a cron job.

